{
  "stem": "27767.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the evening, we went out-- when I went home to sleep, before I went to sleep, I took my father some food, which the SS leftover.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I got some better food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I took him some food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also, I had a few people from my town which I know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I left them potatoes in different places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had-- I hid them in different places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they know where, because I told them where they are going to find it the next day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and [INAUDIBLE], he was joking with me, one of the-- he was a doctor, Dr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we went home, we were liberated, went home back to Romania, he was telling me, how can I pay you back the potatoes?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were laughing always about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And him and some other-- I had about three, four people, another one [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Grun, ?] Eugene [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Grun. ?] And he escaped too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was able to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I find out, my father was a-- he was a tremendous smoker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was smoking at home two packs a day or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was so addicted to smoking, in the camp, from the food what I gave him, he was giving away some of them for cigarettes, for a few for cigarettes, because they were always going down [INAUDIBLE] they were able, some people, have a cigarette or two, and buying a little food for bread or something.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And later, I find out this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father got-- so then I had a little-- I was a little better position, because I wouldn't have survived otherwise, if I wouldn't have been that-- because I remember I had several times diarrhea when I was working.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
